{"tid":1515033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【警超聯】【又入波】【球迷有眼福】休班警涉購K仔　被控藏毒周四提堂","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:54.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9d3314c3103b296d090fa2a5fc9f966274cfbc7c","tid":1515033,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pbh2.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/beautiful-goals-chicharito.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbh2.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F12%2Fbeautiful-goals-chicharito.gif&h=4af99f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n休班警涉購K仔 被控藏毒周四提堂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190828/mobile/bkn-20190828212947871-0828_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190828%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190828212947871-0828_00822_001.html&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=3d133296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190828/mobile/bkn-20190828212947871-0828_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n 今年2月21日下午5時許，警方根據線報在青山龍門路新屯門中心大堂埋伏，期間截查2男1女，在其中一名姓陳(46歲)休班男警員身上，檢獲1.6克K仔，約值660港元，懷疑陳在事發時以現金向一對男女拆家購買K仔。警方以涉嫌藏毒拘捕陳，並以涉嫌販毒拘捕姓蘇(21歲)男子及姓袁(20歲)女子，案件交毒品調查科人員跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，陳曾駐守油尖警區重案組，其後被調往紅磡警署任軍裝警員。警方經調查及諮詢法律意見後，今日(28日)落案控告陳一項藏毒罪，案件明日(29日)上午於屯門裁判法院提堂。警方發言人表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理。"},{"pid":"db59694b271cabfeb33055fde775657cf2da21a1","tid":1515033,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"Ole Ole Ole Ole Ole<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}